# Lift Game

## Description

Lift Game is an interactive simulation game built with JavaScript. The game allows users to simulate the operation of a lift. Users can click on the floor numbers, and the lift moves to the clicked floor. Users can then enter a desired floor number in a modal dialog, and the lift will move to that floor.
The game have 2 Lifts and 8 floors, when the user click on a floor that the lift is close to it, the closest lift will move to that floor, if the lift is not close to the floor, the lift will move to the floor that is close to it and then move to the clicked floor.

